@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About — HD2 Armorer</PageTitle>

<div class="about-page">
    <h1 class="about-heading">About</h1>

    <section class="about-section">
        <p>
            I wanted a quick way to find armor that protects against fire — or gas, acid, or explosives —
            without clicking through every piece in the game. This is that tool.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
        <h2>Credits</h2>
        <p>
            Armor data and images are sourced from
            <a href="https://github.com/Selenestica/hd2-random-strat" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hd2-random-strat</a>
            by <strong>Selenestica</strong>. This project would not exist without their work.
        </p>
        <p>
            The <em>Acclimated</em> passive icon is hand-traced from Helldivers 2 game assets by
            <a href="https://helldivers.wiki.gg/wiki/User:Dogo314" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Dogo314</a>
            via the <a href="https://helldivers.wiki.gg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Helldivers Wiki</a>.
            Used with attribution under Arrowhead Game Studios' EULA.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
        <h2>Resources</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <a href="https://helldivers.wiki.gg/wiki/Helldivers_2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                    Helldivers Wiki
                </a>
                — authoritative reference for armor stats, passives, and acquisition
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>
</div>
